/index.ts` lines 17-29: The `outputs` array declaration should be moved before the `sandbox` object that references it. Currently works due to hoisting semantics but is fragile.\n3. `/workspace/src/deps/index.ts` lines 57-73: `flattenDependencies` includes the root node in results when there are circular dependencies (untested edge case).\n4. `/workspace/src/index.ts` lines 77-79: Unresolvable dependencies are silently skipped rather than failing the installation. This could mask real problems.\n\n**Suggestions (nice to have):**\n\n1. `/workspace/src/index.ts`: Add `semver.valid()` check on `manifest.version` during validation.\n2. `/workspace/src/reviews/index.ts` line 9: Add `Number.isInteger()` check for rating validation.\n3. `/workspace/src/runner/index.ts` line 63: Extract `5000` to a named constant `DEFAULT_TIMEOUT_MS`.\n4. `/workspace/src/deps/index.ts` lines 75-91: `topologicalSort` should defensively handle or document behavior for cyclic graphs.\n5. `/workspace/tests/resolver.test.ts` line 1: Import `beforeEach` explicitly for consistency with other test files.\n6. Add tests for edge cases: duplicate registration, console.error/warn in sandbox, partial dependency resolution, and dependency operations on cyclic graphs."}],"totalDurationMs":125436,"totalTokens":37895,"totalToolUseCount":21,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":279,"cache_read_input_tokens":33198,"output_tokens":4417,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":279,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[]}}}
